Package com.milk.uberchat.irc

Interface Summary
ReplyTap This interface is to be implemented by the taps that are added to snarf away ServerReply messages.
 

Class Summary
CommandMessage This class represents most IRC command messages coming from the host.
CtcpMessage This class encapsulates a CTCP message.
IRCChannel This is the ChatChannel class for IRC channels.
IRCIdentity This is the ChatIdentity class for an IRC identity.
IRCInputFilter This class is a filter on incoming data from an IRC connection.
IRCInteractor This class does all the interaction with an IRC server.
IRCSystem This is the IRC-specific ChatSystem.
IRCSystemTemplate This is the template class for IRCSystems.
IRCUser This is the ChatUser class for an IRC user.
ServerReply This class is for "server reply" type messages, most of which are simple info to pass back to a human, but some of which are actually parseable.
ServerReply.Mapper Helper class used for doing the table mappings.
